'''Solidão''' is a city in the state of [[Pernambuco]], [[Brazil]]. The population in 2009, according with [[Brazilian Institute of Geography and Statistics|IBGE]] was 6.123 inhabitants and the total area is 138.4&nbsp;km².
==Geography==
* State - [[Pernambuco]] * Region - [[Sertão]] Pernambucano * Boundaries - [[Paraiba]] state ('''N''' and '''W'''); [[Afogados da Ingazeira]] and [[Carnaíba]] ('''S'''); [[Tabira, Pernambuco|Tabira]] ('''E'''). * Area - 138.4&nbsp;km² * Elevation - 586 m * Hidrography - [[Pajeú River]] * Vegetation - [[Caatinga]] [[hiperxerófila]] * Clima - [[semi arid]] - ([[Sertão]]) hot * Annual average temperature - 27.0 c * Distance to [[Recife]] - 403.6&nbsp;km
==Economy==
The main economic activities in '''Solidão''' are based in [[agribusiness]], especially creation of [[goat]]s, [[cattle]], [[chickens]]; and plantations of [[maize|corn]] and [[beans]].
